      <event start="T1649-597" end="T668">Da ni sam, </event>
      <event start="T668" end="T669">ja, </event>
      <event start="T669" end="T1650-987">tako. </event>
      <event start="T1673-139" end="T1674-177">Hm. </event>
      <event start="T1677-954" end="T683">Dihur? </event>
      <event start="T683" end="T684">To pa, </event>
      <event start="T684" end="T1681-882">to je [smeh] tako hišni ljubljenček? </event>
      <event start="T1692-818" end="T1693-834">Zanimivo. </event>
      <event start="T1696-545" end="T1698-311">Kaj je imela ona dihurja pol? </event>
      <event start="T1713-019" end="T695">Hja, </event>
      <event start="T695" end="T1714-392">ni š(), ni bila ... </event>
      <event start="T1715-703" end="T1718-595">Ku pa da sta izbrala tako žival za imeti? </event>
      <event start="T1734-982" end="T700">Ma ja, </event>
      <event start="T700" end="T1738-84">prvič tako da bi slišal zdaj za tako reč. </event>
      <event start="T1738-84" end="T1739-593">[glas] </event>
      <event start="T1739-593" end="T703">Ne vem, </event>
      <event start="T703" end="T701">jaz doma nimam nič, </event>
      <event start="T701" end="T702">ne, </event>
      <event start="T702" end="T704">k sem rekel, </event>
      <event start="T704" end="T705">sem v stanovanju zdaj, </event>
      <event start="T705" end="T1743-996">ne vem. </event>
      <event start="T1743-996" end="T706">Mama bi imela kakšnega psa, </event>
      <event start="T706" end="T707">jaz sem bolj od mačk, </event>
      <event start="T707" end="T708">no, </event>
      <event start="T708" end="T710">ma zdaj ne vem, ku bi tata, </event>
      <event start="T710" end="T711">njemu bi bolj ... bi ga bolj motilo, </event>
      <event start="T711" end="T1750-549">ne. </event>
      <event start="T1750-549" end="T1753-164">Če ne pa mačke so mi ful ful v redu. </event>
      <event start="T1753-164" end="T714">Meni je eee res lepa žival, </event>
      <event start="T714" end="T879">zdaj če bi imel za izbirati mačko ali psa, </event>
      <event start="T879" end="T715">bi ... po moje šel za mačko, </event>
      <event start="T715" end="T716">ne, </event>
      <event start="T716" end="T1762-711">čeprav so bolj taki ... ck sebični ... hišni ljubljenčki, </event>
      <event start="T1762-711" end="T717">ne. </event>
      <event start="T717" end="T880">Zdaj pes bo tudi poskrbel zate nazaj, </event>
      <event start="T880" end="T718">če ga boš poskrbel ti za njega, </event>
      <event start="T718" end="T719">ne, </event>
      <event start="T719" end="T1770-634">tako da ... </event>
      <event start="T1780-133" end="T1781-514">Se gulijo nonstop. </event>
      <event start="T1783-039" end="T724">Hm. </event>
      <event start="T724" end="T725">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T725" end="T726">mačke so take, </event>
      <event start="T726" end="T727">se brigajo same zase, </event>
      <event start="T727" end="T1787-494">ne rabiš dati hrano. </event>
      <event start="T1788-048" end="T728">Odvisno, </event>
      <event start="T728" end="T729">ene, ene se hočejo še čohati, </event>
      <event start="T729" end="T1791-803">ne. </event>
      <event start="T1791-803" end="T1792-56">Ene ne. </event>
      <event start="T1795-782" end="T881">So pa res lepa, </event>
      <event start="T881" end="T1798-849">k so prav mičkene, je prav ... </event>
      <event start="T1800-805" end="T1801-674">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T1801-674" end="T735">Tako da, </event>
      <event start="T735" end="T734">ne vem, </event>
      <event start="T734" end="T1806-014">mogoče, k bom imel enkrat svojo hišo. </event>
      <event start="T1806-014" end="T1808-127">Bomo videli, kako bo. </event>
      <event start="T1808-127" end="T1809-733">Eee .. </event>
      <event start="T1813-039" end="T736">Tako da, </event>
      <event start="T736" end="T737">ma ja. </event>
      <event start="T737" end="T738">Zdaj, </event>
      <event start="T738" end="T1817-733">kakšno muziko poslušaš kaj? </event>
      <event start="T1848-253" end="T754">Ti ni pol, </event>
      <event start="T754" end="T755">imaš kakšno zvrst, k ti ni všeč, </event>
      <event start="T755" end="T1853-19">za reči? </event>
      <event start="T1878-474" end="T1880-077">Podeželna glasba. </event>
      <event start="T1880-077" end="T1881-201">Ja, taki. </event>
      <event start="T1882-212" end="T765">Ma jaz sem isto. </event>
      <event start="T765" end="T766">Jaz bolj poslušam vse, kar je, </event>
      <event start="T766" end="T767">mislim, </event>
      <event start="T767" end="T1887-37">zdaj sem bolj te pop muzike. </event>
      <event start="T1887-37" end="T768">Kakšne iz dva tavžent, dvatavžentih let, dva tavžent deset, </event>
      <event start="T768" end="T1892-912">zdaj sem [nerazumljivo] začel poslušati. </event>
      <event start="T1892-912" end="T769">Se malo obudi spomine za nazaj, </event>
      <event start="T769" end="T770">če ne pa, ja, </event>
      <event start="T770" end="T771">isto, </event>
      <event start="T771" end="T772">mislim, </event>
      <event start="T772" end="T1898-237">balkan mi ni problema poslušati. </event>
      <event start="T1898-237" end="T773">Zdaj, </event>
      <event start="T773" end="T774">da bi kakšno zvrst, k prav nnn ne bi maral oziroma rad poslušal, je pa kakšen metal ali pa rok, </event>
      <event start="T774" end="T1906-498">tega mi ... </event>
      <event start="T1907-999" end="T778">tega mi pa res, </event>
      <event start="T778" end="T780">mi hodi skozi uha, da nnn ne morem niti poslušati za rečt, </event>
      <event start="T780" end="T1913-843">ne. </event>
      <event start="T1913-843" end="T1915-396">K mi ... </event>
      <event start="T1918-541" end="T783">Eee </event>
      <event start="T783" end="T784">ja, </event>
      <event start="T784" end="T785">sicer, s() zdaj glih nedavno ... sem bil, </event>
      <event start="T785" end="T786">mislim, </event>
      <event start="T786" end="T787">ni glih koncert, </event>
      <event start="T787" end="T788">smo šli, k je ta DJ, </event>
      <event start="T788" end="T789">ne vem, </event>
      <event start="T789" end="T1927-507">znan. </event>
      <event start="T1927-507" end="T790">Eee </event>
      <event start="T790" end="T791">če ne pa, zdaj da bi šli na koncert, </event>
      <event start="T791" end="T792">gremo poleti, </event>
      <event start="T792" end="T1933-608">na Pagu je en festival. </event>
      <event start="T1933-608" end="T793">In pride dosti takih balkanskih izvajalcev, </event>
      <event start="T793" end="T1938-459">zdaj ... </event>
      <event start="T1938-459" end="T794">Je se zbere dosti ljudi in ... </event>
      <event start="T794" end="T1942-717">v glavnem tako pač </event>
      <event start="T1942-717" end="T1943-546">[glas] </event>
      <event start="T1943-546" end="T795">plac na morju, </event>
      <event start="T795" end="T796">ne, </event>
      <event start="T796" end="T797">in na lesenih na() zan() pač na zzz </event>
      <event start="T797" end="T798">zgrajeno na na morju, </event>
      <event start="T798" end="T1953-511">tako plac in pol ... </event>
      <event start="T1953-511" end="T799">rata v redu, </event>
      <event start="T799" end="T800">no, </event>
      <event start="T800" end="T1956-13">tak dober ambient. </event>
      <event start="T1956-13" end="T801">In se da. </event>
      <event start="T801" end="T1958-704">Mislim ... </event>
      <event start="T1960-812" end="T802">Ma ja, </event>
      <event start="T802" end="T803">dajmo reči, </event>
      <event start="T803" end="T883">da gremo malo prej še, </event>
      <event start="T883" end="T804">da smo malo na morju, </event>
      <event start="T804" end="T805">gremo kaj drugega pogledat, </event>
      <event start="T805" end="T806">dajmo rečt, </event>
      <event start="T806" end="T1968-168">tisti tisto je ene tri dni. </event>
      <event start="T1968-168" end="T884">Mi gremo lahko zdaj ne štiri, pet dni, </event>
      <event start="T884" end="T807">da se gremo tako bolj na komot, </event>
      <event start="T807" end="T1972-997">ne. </event>
      <event start="T1972-997" end="T808">Zdaj ne vem, </event>
      <event start="T808" end="T1975-747">letos planiramo iti dol. </event>
      <event start="T1975-747" end="T809">Bi šli, </event>
      <event start="T809" end="T810">kaj jaz vem, </event>
      <event start="T810" end="T1978-631">po moje v treh. </event>
      <event start="T1978-631" end="T811">Še če gremo, </event>
      <event start="T811" end="T812">če gremo še kakšni poznani dol, </event>
      <event start="T812" end="T1982-912">se itak že dobimo tam. </event>
      <event start="T1982-912" end="T813">[glas] In ... </event>
      <event start="T813" end="T815">tako, </event>
      <event start="T815" end="T814">ne, </event>
      <event start="T814" end="T816">pol bi lahko šli še kam, </event>
      <event start="T816" end="T817">ne, </event>
      <event start="T817" end="T818">da nismo samo na Pagu, </event>
      <event start="T818" end="T819">k zdaj smo že, </event>
      <event start="T819" end="T1991-417">bomo šli v tretje leto že, zaporedoma. </event>
      <event start="T1991-417" end="T1994-505">Bi bilo fajn še kaj kakšen drugi o() hrvaški otok videti. </event>
      <event start="T1998-018" end="T823">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T823" end="T1999-898">ma saj rataš tuf. </event>
      <event start="T1999-898" end="T2001-351">In kaj hočeš? </event>
      <event start="T2002-38" end="T824">Mhm, </event>
      <event start="T824" end="T2003-588">ja. </event>
      <event start="T2003-588" end="T828">Pol je, ku je, </event>
      <event start="T828" end="T2005-585">ne. </event>
      <event start="T2005-585" end="T826">Tako da ... </event>
      <event start="T826" end="T827">to je to, </event>
      <event start="T827" end="T2008-761">ne. </event>
    </tier>
